[ext_resource type="Script" path="res://scripts/houses/house.gd" id="1_house"]

; A blockier, more vibrant cardstock cottage. From the side-camera (+X looking
; -X) the player sees: roof prism + roof trim band + body box + chimney +
; left/right windows + central door with steps. House body and roof colors
; come from the script's exported properties so each instance picks its own.
;
; Note about orientation: the level instantiates the house with a 90° Y-yaw
; so its facade (the door + windows on -Z here) faces the camera (+X world).

